{"tid":2216101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護罷工手足準備俾人秋後算帳","createTime":"2020-09-24T12:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T17:04:00.000Z","uid":147696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0603ced5023ff8c3f85c416e9548f78a9ca1ac84","tid":2216101,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"//醫管局有醫護人員今年 2 月發起罷工，促使港府全面封關，以應對武漢肺炎疫情。醫管局主席范鴻齡早前透露已外聘律師團隊尋求法律意見，以跟進罷工事宜。<br />\n<br />\n范鴻齡今日（24 日）出席醫管局大會後指，已得到律師團隊很詳盡的法律意見，經研究後，會按「合情、合理、合法」的方式跟進，第一步人事部會向當日缺勤的員工發信，查詢他們缺勤原因，涉及數千人，並根據其答覆再作下一步跟進，「邊一個同事採取乜嘢（處分），呢個要睇解釋的程序，今日好難話俾你聽會點做&hellip;」//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3490488841036711/?sfnsn=mo&amp;extid=Z5Bdy0KcbthoxFH3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3490488841036711%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo%26extid%3DZ5Bdy0KcbthoxFH3&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=778e2cbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3490488841036711/?sfnsn=mo&amp;extid=Z5Bdy0KcbthoxFH3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港第3波疫情正正就引證左唔封關既後果!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲打緊仗果陣出咁既消息，范鴻齡，仆你個臭街啦<br />\n<br />\n你要既解釋，當初已經俾哂HR, 我地就係行動一致嫁啦，唔洗一個個問，答案都係一個，要追究既唔該搵返始作俑者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解連登一個熱門post都冇？<br />\n<br />\n順便提埋大家，12位手足好需要我地支持，快d搵位寫返手親筆信俾12位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1841d56c331568c10fa9a1976ae4956242a81e38","tid":2216101,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:15:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3026380f17791363c2ab334475df92d81153e762","tid":2216101,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e616130453e467bcdfcc3476ad9448b5a91fe67c","tid":2216101,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"ec2086465233e1849463dafbd4dbdfad4fe7ab77","tid":2216101,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec1e28533be0d09fddc76469317eda452c95c9b1","tid":2216101,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"084cd22d87258b985f9bef97a313323a734700c2","tid":2216101,"uid":135124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"其實真係好撚心灰 第日到底報唔報HA好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696fdccb130f24706ba9445f207948b0445ea11e","tid":2216101,"uid":147696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"又咁諗，睇你想服侍既對象"},{"pid":"501ae9d97ab974a93bfdbb3912aa671dac8d77f6","tid":2216101,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:43:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"623a47c5498c22655c27a96e9002826c5801fc99","tid":2216101,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫護要撐住呀"}]}